| Term | Definition |
|------|------------|
| Ratio | A comparison of two quantities |
| Proportion | Equality of two ratios |
| Comparison | Determining the relative size of two quantities |
| Fraction | Part of a whole |
| Percent | Percentage representation |
| Equivalent Ratios | Ratios that express the same relation |
| Mean Proportional | Geometric mean of two numbers |

